(\ref{2.1}')}

\medskip
\noindent
Analogously to eq.~(\ref{2.2}), we have spectral parameter dependent
R-matrices for other representations, e.g.
%//{2.12b}
\beq \label{2.12b}
R^{\Lambda_1 \Lambda_1^*}(x/y)=\frac{x}{y}R^{\Lambda_1 \Lambda_1^*}
-\frac{y}{x}P \left( R^{\Lambda_1^* \Lambda_1} \right)^{-1} P.
\eeq
As a spectral parameter dependent version of eq.~(\ref{2.10})
we have crossing relations like
